PERFORMACE PROBLEM
------------------

1. Every performance problem is the RESULT OF A QUEUE BUILDING SOMEWERE...
    > Network socket queue 
    > DB IO queue 
    > OS run queue(thread, CPU availible) etc

2. reason for queue build-up 
    > Inefficient slow processing
    > Serial resouce access
    > Limited resouce capacity  

3. capacity principles
    > Efficiency
    > concurruncy
    > capacity

4. Types of latency & solutions
    > 1.Serial request latency
        > Network latency
            > Data formate & compression, Persistent Connection, Connection pool, session/Data chaching, SSL session chaching 
        > Memory latency
            > avoid memory bloat, weak soft references, multiple smaller process, garbage collection  algorithm      
        > Disk latency
            > chaching, use SSD, Asynchronous I/O, DB optimization, Batch Writes 
        > CPU latency
            > Batch/async I/O, single threaded model, thread pool size, multi process in vertual ENV    
            
    > 2. concurrunce request latency
         

